---
description: Code Style Rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Coding Standards:

- Use TypeScript strictly
- No any type
- Component per file
- Max 300 lines per component

Naming:

Components:
PascalCase

Hooks:
useSomething

Variables:
camelCase

Folders:
kebab-case

Always:

- Add comments for complex logic
- Extract reusable code
- Use async/await